---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Dog-Friendly Walks in the Lake District — A Dog's Guide"
description: "Five dog-friendly walks in the Lake District — from easy tarn loops to open fell summits."
footerType: lake-district
permalink: /lake-district/walks/
---

<div class="dest-intro">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="dest-breadcrumb">
      <a href="/lake-district/"><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></i> Lake District</a>
      <span>›</span> Walks
    </p>
    <h1>Lake District Walks</h1>
    <p class="dest-intro-desc">Five walks your dog will love — from a gentle tarn loop to open fell with long off-lead stretches. All personally selected for dog-friendliness, not just scenery.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="venue-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="itinerary-stops">
      {% for walk in lake_district_walks %}
      <div class="itinerary-stop">
        <p class="itinerary-stop-label">{{ walk.label }}</p>
        <h4>{{ walk.name }}</h4>
        <p>{{ walk.description }}</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted);">{{ walk.subtitle }}</p>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
